<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.3.5">
<l>intuṇaip patumat talarmakaḷ taṉakku miṉpaṉnaṟ puvitaṉak kiṟaivaṉ</l>
<l>tantuṇai yāyar pāvainap piṉṉai taṉakkiṟai maṟṟaiyōrk kellām</l>
<l>vaṉtuṇai pañca pāṇṭavark kāki vāyurai tūtuceṉ ṟiyaṅkum</l>
<l>eṉtuṇai yentai tantaitam māṉait  tiruvallik kēṇi<supplied>k</supplied>kaṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The beloved of [his] sweet friend, the lady of the lotus blossom,</l>
<l>God to the good earth [lady], god to Nappiṉṉai, the girl of his herder friends,</l>
<l>Steadfast friend to all others, my friend who traveled, going [with] a message</l>
<l>By word of mouth for the five Pāṇḍavas, my father’s father’s own,</l>
<l rend="indent">I saw at Tiruvallikkēṇi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
